_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533","description":"一个朋友找我给他推荐键盘，我自己用的不多，而且没有写长文的经历（连续写万字以上），大佬们有没有什么样的键盘适合推荐的？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790741","replies":81,"created_ts":1626829043,"created":"08:57:23","title":"适合写长文的键盘有什么推荐的？","author":"he110comex","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/he110comex","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7c05/2485/490052_mini.png?m=1589765551"},{"id":790747,"node":"iOS","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/ios","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_mini.png?m=1611468295","description":"之前看到过在日本的朋友，要地震了 iPhone 会收到一条地震预警，优先级比普通通知高很多，应该是系统内部向相关机构提供的能力。<br /><br />看到过小米在某些地区推出了地震预警，不知道是不是走的 Android 类似的接口。<br /><br />看到河南这次洪水有感，国内的手机接入这种灾害紧急通知还是有点意义的吧。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790747","replies":80,"created_ts":1626830876,"created":"09:27:56","title":"国内的 iOS 会接入紧急通知系统吗？","author":"pocarisweat","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/pocarisweat","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fde40fc7441030ee57fb96b1b7c1deef?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":790750,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1615111825","description":"<p>在一个地方呆久了就会满格信号也上不了网，需要开关一次飞行模式才能恢复，这种情况自华为被制裁就开始出现了，另一台手机小米就没出现过这种情况，同事的华为也没问题</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790750","replies":78,"created_ts":1626831486,"created":"09:38:06","title":"信号满格，但是上不了网，是运营商的问题还是苹果的问题？","author":"jiayong2793","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jiayong2793","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5ffee50d5547de55dc36405b2d205c49?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":790738,"node":"App Store","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/appstore","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/550a/141f/444_mini.png?m=1531790771","description":"<p>苹果今天正式在国区应用商店内的搜索结果顶部置顶广告，以前一直是没有的。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790738","replies":69,"created_ts":1626828538,"created":"08:48:58","title":"国区 app store 唯一的一个优点今天也没了。","author":"xtx","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xtx","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1266/8b36/439903_mini.png?m=1600317675"},{"id":790732,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1583044904","description":"<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://tb.rg-adguard.net/public.php\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://tb.rg-adguard.net/public.php</a><br /><br />真是太牛逼了。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790732","replies":46,"created_ts":1626820617,"created":"06:36:57","title":"发现一个从官网下载 windows iso 的方法，包括老版本。","author":"guanyin8cnq12","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/guanyin8cnq12","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bc31/47ea/516537_mini.png?m=1625972901"},{"id":790806,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1622572533","description":"<p>目前是公司发的罗技 M110s 有线</p>\n<p>之前用过一些激光的, 还有高 dpi 的, 无线有线都用过</p>\n<p>但感觉都没留下啥深刻印象</p>\n<p>不知道编程的场景, 需要大量阅读文档, 需要大范围移动, 移动精度可以比视觉设计用鼠标低</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790806","replies":43,"created_ts":1626840119,"created":"12:01:59","title":"编程工作适合用什么鼠标?","author":"netwjx","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/netwjx","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/981d/50d6/30219_mini.png?m=1625496250"},{"id":790872,"node":"Python","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/python","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8613/985e/90_mini.png?m=1620107162","description":"<p>代码如下：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-python\"> async def query(self, query, param=None):\n        conn, cur = await self.getCursor()\n        try:\n            await cur.execute(query, param)\n            return await cur.fetchall()\n        except:\n            print('error')\n        finally:\n            if cur:\n                await cur.close()\n            await self.pool.release(conn)\n\n# mysqlobj 是 aiomysql 连接池对象\n\nresult = await asyncio.gather(mysqlobj.query(sql1), mysqlobj.query(sql2), mysqlobj.query(sql3), mysqlobj.query(sql4), mysqlobj.query(sql5))\n\n</code></pre>\n<p>在我的理解中，如果异步执行的话，这段代码执行的时长应该是这 5 个 sql 中耗时最长的时长，但是测试多次，相对同步执行这 5 个 sql 来说，执行时间并没有显著的提升。各位大佬能指点一下吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790872","replies":36,"created_ts":1626855126,"created":"16:12:06","title":"感觉 aiomysql，异步执行多个查询，性能并没有显著的提升啊","author":"ErenJaeger","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ErenJaeger","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f824/a737/414991_mini.png?m=1558599535"},{"id":790761,"node":"小米","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/xiaomi","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_mini.png?m=1584400459","description":"<p>每天不定时挑选几个天选时刻，随机重启....电源键应该是没有问题的，电源键如有有问题的话，日常体验会感觉出来。<br/>\n今天早上马上出地铁闸机了，然后重启了.....<br/>\n日常使用过程中，MIUI 系统也是一堆 BUG，简单列举几个：无故闪屏，无限回退（ A-&gt;B-&gt;A ），莫名其妙弹出 NFC 刷卡界面....果真就是参数没输过，体验没赢过<br/>\n目前系统是 MIUI12.5，现在准备刷个开发板，尝试自救一下。对了，去年 7.2 号买的，过保不到一个月<br/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790761","replies":33,"created_ts":1626832912,"created":"10:01:52","title":"小米 10，过保修期不到 20 天，坏了","author":"afirefish","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/afirefish","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5545/fb37/371735_mini.png?m=1545700054"},{"id":790777,"node":"知乎","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/zhihu","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b789/2fb3/937_mini.png?m=1584298330","description":"今早我在地铁刷着朋友圈，手机被旁边的乘客给撞飞了（ iPhone12 买了就没贴膜和带壳，但也没摔过），手机屏幕没事，边框有几处坑坑哇哇的，对方也说了对不起，我第一反应是屏幕没事就也没说啥，但在路上越想越气，感觉自己都没摔过的手机让别人给摔成战斗成色了。如果我当时要求索赔的话，应如何定损呢？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/790777","replies":29,"created_ts":1626834746,"created":"10:32:26","title":"在地铁里手机被路人撞飞但没碎，要求赔偿是否合理？","author":"VictorFrank1","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/VictorFrank1","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9732/5991/238584_mini.png?m=1499850588"}]